Dameon:
timer for sync
read torrent file to know file contents
ftp/sftp client
watch for file and download until all are present
Download or delete all files based on include/exclude
move and rename based on rule

Client:
reload config  (mva reload)
add item to config (mva add --type horrible --season 2 --eps 0:25 --name "Weebo Dream" --alt "Weebo Baka Desu")
get run history (mva history)
download torrent (mva download/down ./torrentfile.torrent --as/-a alpharatio --exclude/-e "*.nfo" --include/-i "*.mkv" -i "*.mp4")


Config:

{
"plexdir": "/plex",
"torrentdir": "/torrents",
"syncfreq": "1h",
"horrible": {
    "plexsubdir": "anime",
    "remotedir": "/hahah",
    "remotesubdir": "nerow",
    "selector": "\[HorribleSubs\]*.?",
     "shows" : {
        "lala": {
        }
    }
  }
}
